OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThe King and Queen have arrived at the
OL,8,FWhite House for a ceremonial welcome,
OL,9,Fwhere they were greeted by President
OL,10,FDonald Trump and First Lady Melania
OL,11,FTrump.
OL,13,FThe event marks the official arrival
OL,14,Fof the royals on their four-day tour
OL,15,Fof the US, drawing upon a tradition
OL,16,Fthat dates back to the 18th century.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThe arrival ceremony included music by
OL,8,Fthe US Army Herald Trumpets, whilst
OL,9,Fthe national anthems of both countries
OL,10,Fwere played by "The President's Own"
OL,11,FUS Marine Band, with the Presidential
OL,12,FSalute Battery delivering a 21-gun
OL,13,Fsalute.
OL,15,FPresident Trump delivered remarks from
OL,16,Fthe South Lawn following an Inspection
OL,17,Fof the Troops and a Troop in Review,
OL,18,Ffacilitated by the US Army Fife and
OL,19,FDrum Corps.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FHe started his speech by making a
OL,8,Freference to the gloomy, rainy weather
OL,9,Fin Washington DC: "What a beautiful,
OL,10,FBritish day this is."
OL,12,FTrump went on to say that the US has
OL,13,F"no closer friends than the British",
OL,14,Fwhich comes at a time of heightened
OL,15,Ftension in the so-called 'special
OL,16,Frelationship' between the two
OL,17,Fcountries over the US war with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThe president also paid tribute to the
OL,8,Flate Queen Elizabeth, calling her a
OL,9,F"very, very special woman, who is very
OL,10,Fgreatly missed on both sides of that
OL,11,Fmighty Atlantic".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
