PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FAfterwards Trump's speech, both
OL,8,Fcouples stood on the Blue Room
OL,9,FBalcony, to witness a Pass in Review
OL,10,Fof 300 US Service Members and 500
OL,11,Fmembers of the US Armed Forces - an
OL,12,Fhistoric first for state visits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
