PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThousands of guests were gathered on
OL,8,Fthe South Lawn, including members of
OL,9,Fthe president's Cabinet, members of
OL,10,FCongress, the official delegation of
OL,11,Fthe United States of America, the
OL,12,Fofficial delegation of the UK,
OL,13,FAmerican military families and
OL,14,Fstudents from the British
OL,15,FInternational School of Washington.
OL,17,FThe King and Queen will then sign the
OL,18,FWhite House guest book and participate
OL,19,Fin an official gift exchange with the
OL,20,Fpresident and first lady in the Blue
OL,21,FRoom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FLater on, the King will deliver an
OL,8,Fhistoric address to US lawmakers as he
OL,9,Fbecomes only the second monarch in
OL,10,Fhistory to address a joint meeting of
OL,11,Fboth houses of Congress.
OL,13,FHe is expected to offer "the highest
OL,14,Fregard and friendship of the British
OL,15,Fpeople" to the United States during
OL,16,Fhis speech.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FIn a nod to recent tensions over the
OL,8,FUS war in Iran, King Charles will
OL,9,Freflect on the foundations of
OL,10,F"democratic, legal and social
OL,11,Ftraditions" and point out how the two
OL,12,Fnations have stood together throughout
OL,13,Fhistory.
OL,15,FThe monarch is expected to tell
OL,16,FCongress that the nations' "defence,
OL,17,Fintelligence and security ties are
OL,18,Fmeasured not in years but in decades"
OL,19,Fin a tacit acknowledgement of recent
OL,20,Fstrains between Trump and Prime
OL,21,FMinister Keir Starmer.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FCharles will also talk about his
OL,8,Ffaith, and express his belief that in
OL,9,Fthe hearts of the US and UK lies "a
OL,10,Fgenerosity of spirit and a duty to
OL,11,Ffoster compassion, to promote peace,
OL,12,Fto deepen mutual understanding and to
OL,13,Fvalue people of all faiths and none".
OL,15,FHe will note that the story of both
OL,16,Fnations over the last 250 years is one
OL,17,Fof "reconciliation and renewal",
OL,18,Fcalling it "one of the greatest
OL,19,Falliances in human history", which he
OL,20,Fhopes long into the future.
OL,26,@uD@dO]yD@DOUyD@_O]zD@LOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FCharles will also make a brief
OL,8,Freference to the shooting at a
OL,9,FWashington dinner attended by Trump on
OL,10,FSaturday night.
OL,12,FIt will be only the second time a
OL,13,FBritish monarch has addressed a joint
OL,14,Fmeeting of Congress in history, with
OL,15,FQueen Elizabeth becoming the first
OL,16,Fduring a state visit to the US in 1991.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThe royal couple arrived at Joint Base
OL,8,FAndrews, near Washington DC, on Monday
OL,9,Fafternoon, where they were greeted by
OL,10,FUS chief of protocol Monica Crowley
OL,11,Fand the British ambassador to the US,
OL,12,FSir Christian Turner.
OL,14,FThey were then driven in a motorcade
OL,15,Fto the White House, where they were
OL,16,Fmet by the president and first lady
OL,17,Fand shared tea in the Green Room,
OL,18,Fbefore being taken to see the state's
OL,19,Fnewly expanded beehive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FCharles and Camilla then went on to
OL,8,Fattend a traditional garden party at
OL,9,Fthe UK embassy, which was attended by
OL,10,FOlympic diver Tom Daley and Lioness
OL,11,Ffootballer Esme Morgan, along with
OL,12,FSenator Ted Cruz and the current
OL,13,Fspeaker of the house, Mike Johnson.
OL,15,FAlso among the guests at the garden
OL,16,Fparty were women from groups
OL,17,Fcampaigning against domestic violence
OL,18,Fand violence against women and girls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777420987
OL,3,CTrump rolls out red carpet for King
OL,4,Cand Queen at White House ceremonial
OL,5,Cwelcome
OL,7,FThere had been calls for the King and
OL,8,FQueen to meet survivors of convicted
OL,9,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein but the
OL,10,Fpalace has avoided this over concerns
OL,11,Fabout legal processes surrounding
OL,12,Fongoing investigations.
OL,14,FThis is Talking Royals - our weekly
OL,15,Fpodcast about the Royal Family, with
OL,16,FITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship and
OL,17,FProducer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
